      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this stunning vehicle that is in absolute mint condition! It looks and feels brand new, with a flawless exterior and an interior that still has that fresh-from-the-factory smell. This is a rare find for anyone seeking a truly pristine car that has been meticulously maintained and cared for\u2014truly a showroom-quality gem ready for its next owner!",
