    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a dependable daily driver or a solid starting point for a restoration project. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat, though there is no major structural damage. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows signs of wear on the upholstery and some minor cosmetic aging on the dashboard. Mechanically, it remains reliable and starts up without issue, though it may eventually benefit from some routine maintenance to keep it running smoothly.",
      "price": 19500.0,
